{"tid":666964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對抗日本絕美「櫻花河」　陸網友發現最新秘境「抹茶河」","createTime":"2018-05-16T10:34:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T11:21:55.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1519,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":107,"replies":[{"pid":"102653ca1218283fd4350a56f5bd1030e46f4b93","tid":666964,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T10:34:11.000Z","msg":"大陸中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n近日日本櫻花盛開，許多著名賞櫻景點也出現大量觀光客，為了對抗這波「旅行潮」，有中國大陸網友就分享最新秘境，並取名為「抹茶河」，讓其他網友瘋狂詢問「這在哪裡！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/05/16/1361620-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F1361620-XXL.jpg&h=b238fbe9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲日本櫻花河超美。（圖／翻攝自微博）</span><br />\n<br />\n日本知名景點「目黑川八幡宮」，在河川旁種下滿滿的櫻花樹，除了盛開的櫻花樹讓各國旅客朝聖外，河川上飄著滿滿的櫻花也是該處景點的特別之處，有中國大陸網友不堪示弱，貼出自己發現的秘境「抹茶河」，引起網友瘋傳。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/05/16/1361621-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F1361621-XXL.jpg&h=299db786&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲中國大陸「抹茶河」讓人看得心慌。（圖／翻攝自微博）</span><br />\n<br />\n網友們看完後都說「差別就是一個香、一個臭」、「這污染看得我心慌」、「你這樣我以後怎麼面對抹茶」、「沒看大圖我差點以為是真的」、「這張圖為什麼有味道？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=380500\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D380500&d=YyqeJoGqwpmQPnUJQVY3cDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=3cc27e76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D380500&h=71192221\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=380500</a>"},{"pid":"6719048350c14f37c4bcbb37c0c2ccf43167eb62","tid":666964,"uid":33463,"like":114,"dislike":2,"score":112,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T10:35:27.000Z","msg":"又然"},{"pid":"af1a034ad95ad7a0a5924a52f5bb3622d0d553b8","tid":666964,"uid":39012,"like":5,"dislike":